        FAMRecord represents the data fields that the user would store in a persistent datastore.
        Parameters:
        svc - Service code such as session or saml2
        op - Operation such as read, write, delete, deletebydate.
        pKey - Primary Key
        eDate - Expiration Date
        secKey - Secondary Key
        st - state
        ax - Additional Data
        serializedInternalSessionBlob - Binary Blob
